    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034720/extras/f36ad133fcd24b666b51c7af1310483f.poster.avif?t=1762453607\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034720/extras/f36ad133fcd24b666b51c7af1310483f.webm?t=1762453607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034720/extras/f36ad133fcd24b666b51c7af1310483f.mp4?t=1762453607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在序章中，您将能够体验到 Tavern Manager Simulator 的限量版。不要忘记将其添加到您的愿望清单并关注我们以获取完整版游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034720/extras/607981ebae79a5941ce3798c1ede75ef.avif?t=1762453607\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>恢复酒馆</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接管幻想王国中一家废弃的酒馆，并将其恢复到昔日的辉煌！清除垃圾和蜘蛛网，擦去灰尘，购买新家具和装饰，并根据自己的喜好布置这个地方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034720/extras/2537f375e8213f3e6752cac3d22c5e68.poster.avif?t=1762453607\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034720/extras/2537f375e8213f3e6752cac3d22c5e68.webm?t=1762453607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034720/extras/2537f375e8213f3e6752cac3d22c5e68.mp4?t=1762453607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>服务您的客户</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速优质的客户服务是酒馆繁荣的关键。所有顾客都希望他们的桌子上能同时摆满啤酒和开胃菜，就像变魔术一样。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034720/extras/3f78b258879f80c10d0bcb81f3d2f8a5.poster.avif?t=1762453607\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034720/extras/3f78b258879f80c10d0bcb81f3d2f8a5.webm?t=1762453607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034720/extras/3f78b258879f80c10d0bcb81f3d2f8a5.mp4?t=1762453607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>功能</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在幻想王国中经营您废弃的酒馆</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >翻新、改善、扩大您的机构</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将啤酒倒入大杯子</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打扫、洗碗</p></li></ul>",
